## Summary
Predictions in Amplitude Activation use AI to segment users based on their likelihood to perform future actions, helping optimize targeting workflows for maximum lift in communication frequency, dynamic pricing, and content personalization by employing a transformer-based sequence model that analyzes events, properties, and user activity sequences to calculate probabilistic scores.

